      <description>&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;

&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;;baseurl;/img/actions/question.svg&#34; alt=&#34;Icon&#34; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Check if you closely followed the instructions&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Our &lt;a href=&#34;;baseurl;support/firststeps#making-a-live-system&#34;&gt;first steps guide&lt;/a&gt; provides you further information&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;;baseurl;/img/actions/warning.svg&#34; alt=&#34;Icon&#34; /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Maybe your computer needs to be configured to be able to boot&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;

&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Some manufacturers have by default disabled booting from other devices. If this is the case, you can refer to following information:&lt;/td&gt;
